=== GPCR Autoantibody Cascade (β2-AR, M2/M4 mAChR)
  <sec:gpcr-cascade>

*Certainty: 0.55.* GPCR autoantibodies documented across ME/CFS, POTS, and Long COVID. Functional pathogenicity confirmed by bioassay and animal passive transfer (β2-AR AAb infusion in rats reproduces POTS phenotype). Germain 2025 null by Luminex raises assay-sensitivity question — bioassay-positive patients may be Luminex-negative. *Receptor roles in this cascade:* β2-AR (beta-2 adrenergic receptor) mediates vasodilation, lipolysis, and mast cell stabilization; M2/M4 mAChR (muscarinic ACh receptors) mediate vagal cardiac control (M2) and CNS cholinergic signalling (M4); α1-AR (alpha-1 adrenergic receptor) mediates vasoconstriction on vascular smooth muscle.

